nixpkgs / isabelle - Isabelle is a generic proof assistant. It allows mathematical formulas to be expressed in a formal language and provides tools for proving those formulas in a logical calculus.

Homepage - https://isabelle.in.tum.de/

License - BSD-3-Clause

Maintainers - John Wiegley
